There will always be haters, doubters, and non-believers. They will say you can't make it, that you can't have what you want. And then there will be you, PROVING THEM WRONG. One of the Best Motivational Speeches Ever featuring Coach Pain (https://bit.ly/CoachPainMotiversity).
